Class FisaMedicala

java.lang.Object
vet.system1.FisaMedicala
public class FisaMedicala extends Object
Represents a medical record for an animal. Contains details such as the record ID, doctor ID, animal ID, diagnostic, treatment recommendations, and appointment date.
